byline.original: By MIKE ISAAC and LESLIE PICKER

abstract: Shares of mobile-payments startup Square surge by 45 percent after initial public offering, closing day at $13.07.
lead_paragraph: A positive start for the newly public payments company is a hopeful sign for the struggling tech I.P.O. market.

headline.main: Shares of Square Soar by 45% After Public Offering
